/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a bustling street in Beijing, China. The vantage point is high, providing a bird's eye view of the scene below. The street is flanked by buildings on both sides, their facades bathed in the soft glow of the setting sun. Trees line the street, their leaves rustling gently in the breeze. Power lines crisscross above, forming a network of veins that pulsate with the life of the city. Cars are parked neatly on the side of the road, their metallic bodies gleaming under the sunlight. The sky above is a clear blue, with the sun setting in the distance, casting long shadows and bathing everything in a warm, golden light. The image is a beautiful blend of urban architecture and natural elements, a snapshot of life in a bustling city.
